EDIT:

Does anyone have a mohawk that's over three inches in length? My mum cut my hair for me Friday (photos later) and it's a mohawk once styled properly, but the shit that I have is just that. Shit. And it doesn't work, my 'hawk don't stay up! And most hair products are real expensive these days. We're gonna trim it a little more and see if that makes any difference, but I was just wondering if anyone knew of any good products that work with mohawks; some of them are huge! How the hell do they stay up?! Any help is greatly appreciated. =]

To anyone it may concern, My sidekick died. X'( I cried, dude. It's fucking upsetting. Anyray, this means that I won't be online (MSN, Yahoo) 24/7 like I usually am. It also means that I'll probably get behind a lot on reading stories as I do most of that from my sidekick (that also includes writing =S). The only time I will be online is if I am able to get on the computer, unless, of course, by beloved phone is fixable. I'm taking the poor thing in tomorrow to see if they can fix it - hopefully they can. I'm definately crossing my fingers. Just thought that I would let you guys know. Love, Me. ♥xoxo
